  "text": "The biogenicity of the Farrel Quartzite microfossils (lenses, spheres and films) has been demonstrated by a series of studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] [CITATION_8] . Here we summarise the lines of evidence as follows:",
